{"expireTime":9007200804686286000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-ast-a63e06516bf264304c540f2362a89f7b-gatsby-remark-graphvizgatsby-remark-code-titlesgatsby-remark-imagesgatsby-remark-responsive-iframegatsby-remark-autolink-headersgatsby-remark-prismjsgatsby-remark-copy-linked-filesgatsby-remark-smartypants-","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gatsby does an incredible amount of cool stuff for you, automatically. This makes Gatsby an incredibly powerful, versatile tool. However, this broad depth of functionality can make it difficult to explain what Gatsby does in a concise and approachable way.","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":257,"offset":257},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":257,"offset":257},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"In this post, I’ll aim for the latter — an approachable explanation of what Gatsby does using a series of analogies that others have found helpful. I hope you do, too!","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":259},"end":{"line":4,"column":169,"offset":427},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":259},"end":{"line":4,"column":169,"offset":427},"indent":[]}},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"loose":false,"children":[{"type":"listItem","loose":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Start off with a pre-configured development environment and build process (high-performance car)","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":4,"offset":432},"end":{"line":6,"column":100,"offset":528},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":4,"offset":432},"end":{"line":6,"column":100,"offset":528},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":429},"end":{"line":6,"column":100,"offset":528},"indent":[]}},{"type":"listItem","loose":false,"checked":null,"c